title: Cyber Punk Compilation Volume 2
description:
Cyberpunk is a science fiction genre noted for its focus on "high tech and low life", featuring advanced technology and cybernetics, coupled with a degree of breakdown or radical change in the social order. Some musicians have been classified as cyberpunk due to their aesthetic style and musical content. Often dealing with dystopian visions of the future or biomechanical themes, some fit more squarely in the category than others.
